data.description: Welcome home to this cozy 3 Bedroom, 1.5 bath in North Scranton. Nestled in a beautiful neighborhood, this home makes a perfect starter home with an inviting family room and a lovely and large open-kitchen to socialize with your friends and family. Step outside to the lovely deck and a pretty yard as you sip and savor your favorite beverage. Fenced in yard that would be perfect for pet lovers and homeowners to explore various hobbies. Won't last long.
